This paper deals with the analysis of language and semantics, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of probabilistic frameworks and formal methods also suggests that it could belong to the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with the analysis of composite systems, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of Computational Complexity (cs.CC) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
